{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require businesses give staff the option to be paid monthly",
        "additional_details": "Being paid every four weeks, rather than monthly, can make it more difficult to manage personal finances. It can be a particular issue for people claiming Universal Credit, leading to loss of benefits when a claimant is paid twice in a month.",
        "background": "We want the Government to require all businesses to give their staff the option to be paid monthly, to help people manage their finances.",
